{"tid":1862604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"炒價賣口罩仲要扮好人","createTime":"2020-02-04T17:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T21:57:52.000Z","uid":190304,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"094594161db6a4295b958adf91fe681c6d6ae9b9","tid":1862604,"uid":190304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNnppmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNnppmj.jpg&h=8ddeb1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOGp8OX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOGp8OX.png&h=cfecedcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實已經睇唔過眼好耐<br />\n由反送中嘅時候扮黃<br />\npost返送中嘅新聞 講到自己有幾嬲<br />\n講真三罷嘅時候都唔見有罷過市<br />\n用人地條命幫自己賣廣告<br />\n<br />\n今日一罩難求 話幫大家揾口罩<br />\n隔離藥房都係賣緊百幾蚊盒<br />\n點解仲可以講到自己好好人咁</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKR5TiP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKR5TiP.png&h=675e67d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢問執紙皮嘅婆婆同賺唔到錢嘅人冇口罩點算<br />\n咁好人唔見你派比佢地？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Follow本店者優先啊 我係唔係要代執紙皮婆婆follow你間shop啊？</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以收收皮 好嘔心</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bf6079900e9cd0c2a2df758a20f731d08f82dcdf","tid":1862604,"uid":13288,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"個盒都溶溶爛爛咁 成本價應該10蚊左右 賣貴20倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1423a6804b5c7e89c0618a94375d23a54e5b1f","tid":1862604,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:21:19.000Z","msg":"200應該都只係賺少少<br />\n（唔知成本幾多 唔好屌我）"},{"pid":"439bf4e9024e3dbe68cb366427fa775248dd0147","tid":1862604,"uid":3318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T17:22:37.000Z","msg":"佢來貨